啲女staff 幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f56ca27b0e32ba1cfc7fd70f765783bbe7f712f3","tid":522111,"uid":59794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:39:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>利申：做過好短時間<br />\n3-4年前就11000/mth （冇記錯嘅話）<br />\n有medical benefit，睇醫生可claim 錢，資助睇牙醫等等（你可以問清楚HR）<br />\n<br />\n但係日日返工會好似冇晒私人時間咁<br />\n永世唔可準時收工<br />\n亦冇固定返工時間（即係可以今日改咗你聽日返工時間）<br />\n<br />\nOT 1個鐘之後先補水<br />\n但有啲閪上司就要你做到50mins 就放你走</blockquote>平時返工有咩做？</blockquote><br />\n一般就執整齊啲嘢，fill滿晒啲架<br />\n轉貨，serve 客<br />\n叫下welcome Muji <br />\n朝早返工就到晨操、收貨同briefing<br />\n夜晚收工就執整齊成個場<br />\n<br />\nBtw 放心，返工前有training 要上，大概講解成個返工流程"},{"pid":"1685db2517e1eaf7a688719d6d230de968cb94d0","tid":522111,"uid":59794,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:40:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時見到 無印啲女staff 幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放過我哋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2013f607a6c2662146ccd0622056f8e721895e0","tid":522111,"uid":74435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T06:40:57.000Z","msg":"咪撚做日本公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826b12681fdee96d6f9ed0bfa97264be957308f8","tid":522111,"uid":51673,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5cd0362f54df2c5405c5e891df40293298a90833","tid":522111,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5c412444ebd5b72c3e3443237e12d8aa925e892","tid":522111,"uid":51673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44a5ab8005cf8e2a69b9ab926199d00c09da1816","tid":522111,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited